<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>kecaripa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nmarkku yāṇṭu 8 Āvatu Aṭi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kaḷ paḻuveṭṭar<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> yar maṟavankaṇṭaṉā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ā kanmi kunṟakkūṟṟattu Āṟaṇi nallūruṭ<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yān maṉapperum<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> cuvāmiyāṉa kunṟanā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭṭu kaṇṭaperuntiṇaiyār ciṟupaḻuvūr ti
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ruvālantuṟ<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> ma<hi rend="grantha">hād[e</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">]</hi> <supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku ca
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ntirā<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>di</unclear></hi> ttaval Iravum paka<unclear>lu</unclear>m Oru
<lb n="9"/>nontāviḷakku Eriya vaitta ney nārā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>yattāl nicata muḻakku Uḻakkukkum vai tta cā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vā mūvāp perāṭu toṇṇūṟu Itu
<lb n="12"/>pa<hi rend="grantha">nmā heśvara rakṣai</hi> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
